events.name: Breakthrough Metagrating Tech Filters Light with Unprecedented Precision—A Game Changer for Advanced Imaging
events.description: Scientists have made a groundbreaking discovery in the field of augmented reality (AR), sensors, and imaging technology. Researchers at a leading university have developed a 'metagrating' filter that selectively filters light based on both wavelength and angle, effectively unlocking new possibilities for next-generation applications.

events.name: Did the millennium falcon land there or what’s going on? Australia 🇦🇺 UFO UAP sighting news. 📰
events.description: A bizarre UFO sighting in the Australian outback has left experts stunned, as a Millennium Falcon from Star Wars appears to have landed in the desert. According to witnesses, the ship's landing gear is intact and its distinctive design features are evident. However, it remains unexplained how the object ended up in this location, with some speculating it may be a military craft or a prank gone wrong. Further investigation is needed to verify these claims.
